%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fschool-classrooms-around-the-world-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20attending%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-public-high-schools-in-america-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20school%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20suburban%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fglad-i-accidentally-went-to-ohio-university-instead-of-florida-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOhio%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20experience%20living%20in%20the%20megacity%20of%20New%20Delhi%20and%20navigating%20the%20school%20system%20here%20vastly%20differs%20from%20what%20I%20grew%20up%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20my%20firsthand%20perspectives%20on%20the%20disparities%20between%20schools%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFormal%20schooling%20starts%20early%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20striking%20differences%20I%20noticed%20is%20the%20age%20at%20which%20formal%20schooling%20begins%20for%20children%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20case%2C%20my%20kids%20started%20in%20a%20formal%20pre-K%20program%20when%20they%20were%203%20years%20old.%20The%20immense%20demand%20for%20quality%20education%2C%20especially%20in%20India's%20cities%2C%20where%20competition%20for%20school%20admission%20is%20fierce%2C%20drives%20this%20early%20start.%20This%20leads%20to%20the%20prevailing%20notion%20that%20if%20you%20don't%20enroll%20your%20child%20in%20the%20formal%20school%20system%20early%2C%20you%20might%20miss%20the%20window%20of%20opportunity%20to%20secure%20a%20spot%20in%20one%20of%20the%20more%20coveted%20institutions%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20get%20into%20some%20schools%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchool%20admissions%20in%20New%20Delhi%20are%20a%20high-stakes%20endeavor%2C%20unlike%20the%20public-school%20system%20I%20grew%20up%20with%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20your%20address%20mostly%20dictates%20which%20school%20you%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20admissions%20process%20here%20is%20complex%20and%20multifaceted%2C%20incorporating%20factors%20such%20as%20proximity%20to%20the%20school%C2%A0and%20alumni%20status.%20But%20schools%20also%20consider%20things%20like%20parents'%20education%20levels%2C%20giving%20preference%20to%20better-educated%20parents%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20may%20signal%20the%20family%20prioritizes%20education.%20Even%20factors%20like%20a%20child's%20gender%20are%20taken%20into%C2%A0consideration.%20Historically%20in%20India%2C%20many%20families%20prioritized%20the%20education%20of%20sons%20over%20that%20of%20daughters%20because%20the%20sons%20would%20continue%20to%20care%20for%20their%20parents%20in%20old%20age.%20Schools%2C%20in%20awarding%20additional%20points%20in%20admissions%20consideration%20to%20girls%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20advocate%20for%20girls'%20education%20and%20correct%20that%20longstanding%20gender%20bias.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20students%20meet%20these%20criteria%2C%20schools%20select%20them%20through%20lotteries.%20The%20acceptance%20rates%20at%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20schools%20are%20staggeringly%20low%2C%20hovering%20at%20around%201%25.%20The%20pressure%20on%20parents%20to%20secure%20their%20child's%20admission%20begins%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20this%20intense%20competition%20can%20be%20incredibly%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20are%20more%20one-day%20school%20holidays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20growing%20up%20with%20leisurely%20summer%20and%20winter%20breaks%20that%20ranged%20from%20three%20weeks%20to%20three%20months%20in%20length.%20My%20kids%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20only%20enjoy%20a%20six-week%20summer%20hiatus%20from%20mid-May%20to%20late%20June%2C%20and%20a%2010-day%20break%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Indian%20school%20calendar%20compensates%20with%20frequent%20one-day%20holidays%20throughout%20the%20year.%20These%20single-day%20%26quot%3Bchuttis%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bholidays%26quot%3B%20in%20Hindi%20%E2%80%94%20encompass%20an%20array%20of%20religious%20and%20public%20holidays%2C%20including%20Eid%2C%20Christmas%2C%20Buddha's%20Birthday%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20birthday%2C%20Diwali%2C%20various%20Hindu%20gods'%20birthdays%2C%20Sikh%20gurus'%20birthdays%2C%20and%20national%20holidays%20such%20as%20Independence%20Day%20and%20Republic%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20kids%20are%20learning%20several%20languages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Indian%20schools%20adopt%20a%20bilingual%20approach%20to%20education.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20instructors%20teach%20our%20kids%20in%20English%2C%20our%20kids%20have%20studied%20Hindi%20since%20kindergarten%2C%20and%20they'll%20begin%20learning%20a%20third%20foreign%20language%20in%20the%20fourth%20grade.%20This%20multilingual%20approach%20reflects%20the%20diverse%20linguistic%20landscape%20of%20India%20and%20prepares%20students%20to%20communicate%20effectively%20in%20both%20a%20country%20as%20diverse%20as%20India%20and%20in%20the%20wider%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20more%20emphasis%20on%20STEM%20subjects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20schools%20place%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20STEM%20subjects.%20While%20they%20do%20teach%20basic%20grammar%2C%20there%20is%20often%20less%20emphasis%20on%20reading%20full%20books%20as%20part%20of%20the%20curricula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20children's%20English%20textbooks%2C%20there%20are%20excerpts%20from%20works%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BAlice's%20Adventures%20in%20Wonderland%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTreasure%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jungle%20Book%3Cem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20teachers%20assign%20few%20full%20novels%20as%20reading.%20In%20contrast%2C%20in%20his%20environmental-studies%20class%2C%20my%20fifth%20grader%20is%20delving%20into%20topics%20including%20human%20and%20plant%20anatomy%20that%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20until%20my%20freshman%20year%20of%20college%20in%20t