0show%20off%20the%20Cybertruck's%20unbreakable%20windows%20at%20its%202019%20unveiling%2C%20is%20currently%20on%20sale%20for%20%2455%20on%20Tesla's%20online%20store.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40insider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ybertruck-decal-inspired-elon-musks-famous-window-smashing-incident-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Fill%20up%20the%20Entire%20Canvas%E2%80%99%3A%20Amol%20Palekar%20on%20Embracing%20His%20Journey%20in%20Visual%20Arts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01172550%2Fimage-1566.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20November%2C%20at%20the%20Jehangir%20Art%20Gallery%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20that%20actor%2C%20director%2C%20and%20painter%2C%20Amol%20Palekar%20opened%20his%20solo%20show%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Through%20the%20Radiance%E2%80%99.%20Curated%20by%20film%20director%20and%20Palekar%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Sandhya%20Gokhale%2C%20it%20is%20a%20series%20of%20abstract%20works%20interspersed%20with%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20%3Cem%3Ekavad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20storytelling%20tool%20with%20panels%20that%20aid%20a%20narrative.%20The%20lighting%20is%20focused%20and%20cinematic%2C%20and%20the%20canvases%20are%20framed%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20adds%20depth%20to%20the%20paintings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalekar%2C%20who%20graduated%20from%20the%20JJ%20School%20of%20Arts%2C%20started%20out%20as%20a%20painter%20with%20his%20first%20solo%20show%20in%201967.%20It%20was%20in%20the%20same%20year%20that%20he%20took%20his%20first%20steps%20in%20theatre%20through%20%3Cem%3EChup!%20Court%20Chalu%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20in%20film%20with%20Govind%20Nihalani%20and%20Satyadev%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EShantata!%20Court%20Chalu%20Aahe%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20two%20back%20to%20back%20hits%20in%20Hindi%20films%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ERajnigandha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1974)%20and%20%3Cem%3EChhoti%20Si%20Baat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1976)%2C%20Palekar%2C%20a%20well-known%20name%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20stage%2C%20became%20a%20nationally%20known%20name%2C%20playing%20an%20Everyman%20character%20whom%20the%20middle%20classes%20could%20identify%20with.%20Paintings%20took%20a%20backseat%20and%20Palekar%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20made%20of%20the%20stage%20and%20film%20sets.%20He%20played%20memorable%20roles%20and%20was%20a%20regular%20in%20Basu%20Chatterjee%E2%80%99s%20and%20Hrishikesh%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20films.%20Palekar%20terms%20this%20period%20in%20his%20life%20as%20his%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20on%20to%20his%20second%2C%20since%202014%2C%20Palekar%20is%20back%20to%20painting%20with%20renewed%20vigour%20and%20armed%20with%20his%20learnings%20from%20the%20performing%20arts.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20difference%20between%20the%20performing%20arts%2Fcinema%2C%20and%20visual%20arts%20is%20that%20in%20the%20former%2C%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20communicate%20with%20another%20person%2C%20and%20presenting%20your%20art.%20With%20visual%20arts%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20inward%20journey.%20It%E2%80%99s%20diametrically%20opposite%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20wisdom%20in%20performing%20arts%20and%20cinema%20gave%20me%20quite%20a%20few%20insights%20for%20this%20inward%20journey.%20It%20has%20made%20me%20richer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20tells%20us%2C%20is%20especially%20true%2C%20of%20his%20last%20exhibition%2C%20where%20he%20has%20become%20more%20confident%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20need%20to%20say%20too%20much.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20theatre%2C%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20hold%20a%20pause.%20In%20between%20two%20lines%2C%20the%20pause%20that%20I%20hold%20is%20completely%20my%20victory%20as%20an%20actor.%20Not%20saying%20anything%20and%20yet%20being%20expressive%20is%20something%20I%20brought%20back%20to%20my%20second%20innings%20in%20visual%20arts.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20fill%20up%20the%20entire%20canvas.%20I%20am%20not%20scared%20of%20having%20said%20just%20a%20little.%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20the%20unspoken%20that%20you%20convey%20through%20a%20pause%20or%20texture%2C%20is%20powerful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170013%2Fimage-1561.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221131%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170013%2Fimage-1561.png%201131w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170013%2Fimage-1561-300x198.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170013%2Fimage-1561-1024x676.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687286%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20fill%20up%20the%20entire%20canvas.%20I%20am%20not%20scared%20of%20having%20said%20just%20a%20little%2C%E2%80%99%20says%20Amol%20Palekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalekar%20uses%20the%20medium%20of%20oil%20paints%20that%20is%20both%20rigid%20and%20difficult%20to%20work%20with.%20He%20finds%20acrylic%20too%20synthetic%2C%20Gokhale%20steps%20in%20to%20say.%20His%20current%20work%20is%20not%20just%20visually%20different%20but%20technically%20accomplished%2C%20too.%20His%20brush%20strokes%20are%20stronger%20and%20more%20confident%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20colour%20is%20exuberant%2C%20without%20giving%20in%20to%20the%20loud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPainted%20during%20the%20pandemic%20that%20the%20duo%20chose%20to%20spend%20in%20their%20Pune%20home%2C%20these%20works%2C%20Palekar%20tells%20us%2C%20were%20an%20attempt%20to%20find%20the%20ray%20of%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20His%20use%20of%20black%20canvases%20and%20hues%20like%20red%2C%20orange%2C%20green%2C%20and%20cobalt%20blue%2C%20speak%20of%20this%20duality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20reflective%20of%20how%20I%20dealt%20with%20the%20pandemic.%20If%20we%20think%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%20completely%20dark%20and%20full%20of%20depression%20and%20pessimism.%20It%20was%20like%20being%20in%20a%20gigantic%20tunnel%2C%20you%20see%20nothing%2C%20and%20you%20feel%20nothing.%20You%20have%20no%20clue%20when%20or%20if%20this%20will%20end.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20chose%20black%20canvas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20there%20is%20always%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20started%20facing%20the%20black%20canvas%20and%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20light%20that%20will%20give%20us%20hope%2C%20relief%2C%20and%20exuberance.%20The%20canvas%20started%20talking%20to%20me%2C%20through%20bright%20colours%20and%20bold%20strokes.%20I%20started%20exploring%20that%20feeling%20of%20joy%20and%20celebration%20that%20one%20needs%20to%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkin%20to%20an%20earlier%20series%20of%20paintings%20titled%20%E2%80%98Trickles%E2%80%99%2C%20Palekar%E2%80%99s%20mastery%20of%20oil%20paint%20has%20enabled%20him%20to%20infuse%20in%20it%20a%20watercolour-like%20ability.%20The%20trickles%20of%20paint%2C%20streaming%20down%20are%20nearly%20translucent.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20this%20focus%20on%20texture%2C%20technique%2C%20and%20brush%20strokes%20that%20makes%20this%20series%20different%20from%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gokhale%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01171810%2Fimage-1564.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22757%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01171810%2Fimage-1564.png%20757w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01171810%2Fimage-1564-300x298.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01171810%2Fimage-1564-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687293%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20picture%20from%20Amol%20Palekar%E2%80%99s%20exhibition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalekar%E2%80%99s%20abstraction%20carries%20forward%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekavads%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20act%20as%20companion%20pieces%20to%20some%20of%20the%20paintings.%20They%20are%20extensions%20of%20the%20same%20strokes%20and%20colours%2C%20with%20varied%20surface%20areas%20that%20add%20a%20hint%20of%20drama.%20Palekar%20tells%20us%20that%20his%20process%20involved%20a%20canvas%20and%20the%20accompanying%20%3Cem%3Ekavad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebefore%20he%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Ekavad%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20fascinated%20him%20from%20the%20time%20he%20made%20%3Cem%3EPaheli%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20he%20directed%20based%20on%20Vijaydan%20Detha%E2%80%99s%20story%20%3Cem%3EDuvidha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20that%20made%20him%20travel%20to%20the%20interiors%20of%20Rajasthan.%20This%20is%20another%20instance%20of%20his%20work%20in%20film%20seeping%20into%20the%20realm%20of%20the%20visual%20arts.%20For%20Palekar%20though%2C%20it%20has%20all%20been%20a%20seamless%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20notice%20the%20films%20I%20have%20directed%2C%20my%20visual%20search%20for%20spaces%2C%20locations%2C%20and%20forms%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20painter%20in%20me.%20You%20can%20also%20see%20the%20performer%20in%20me.%20It%20has%20all%20blended%20well%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170910%2Fimage-1563.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221112%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170910%2Fimage-1563.png%201112w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170910%2Fimage-1563-300x155.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01170910%2Fimage-1563-1024x529.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687290%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPalekar%E2%80%99s%20abstraction%20carries%20forward%20in%20kavads%20that%20act%20as%20companion%20pieces%20to%20some%20of%20the%20paintings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20had%20left%20the%20JJ%20School%20of%20Arts%2C%20Palekar%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20representative%20painting%20had%20vanished.%20He%20has%20explored%20abstract%20art%20from%20his%20first%20exhibition%20and%20says%20that%20he%20finds%20it%20far%20more%20enriching.%20He%20does%2C%20however%2C%20lament%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20find%20the%20form%20unapproachable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20understanding%20art%20a%20pre-condition%3F%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20know%20what%20%3Cem%3Eraga%20%3C%2Fem%3Emusic%20is%20based%20on%20to%20enjoy%20it.%20We%20respond%20to%20poetry%20easily%20even%20though%20it%20goes%20beyond%20words.%20But%2C%20we%20unfortunately%2C%20as%20a%20society%2C%20are%20not%20exposed%20to%20forms%20of%20visual%20arts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20dialogue%20and%20conversations%20through%20his%20exhibitions%20help%20him%20bridge%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20there%20are%20times%2C%20when%20the%20response%20to%20his%20works%20of%20abstraction%20leaves%20him%20overwhelmed.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20not%20from%20a%20city%20boy%20one%20could%20tell.%20He%20went%20very%20close%20to%20one%20of%20the%20paintings%20and%20spent%20half%20an%20hour%20looking%20at%20it.%20Sandhya%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20was%20intrigued%20by%20the%20texture.%20She%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20was%20a%20painter.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20never%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20but%20after%20this%2C%20he%20felt%20like%20the%20painting%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Palekar%2C%20narrating%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701437408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fi-dont-fill-up-the-entire-canvas-amol-palekar-on-embracing-his-journey-in-visual-arts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20November%2C%20Palekar%20opened%20his%20solo%20show%2C%20titled%20'Through%20the%20Radiance'%2C%20which%20is%20a%20series%20of%20abstract%20works%20interspersed%20with%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20'kavad'%2C%20a%20storytelling%20tool%20with%20panels%20that%20aid%20a%20narrative.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20red%20carpet%20for%20Tesla%20in%20India%3F%20What%20govt%20official%20said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701437317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105660241%2Cimgsize-40068.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fno-special-red-carpet-for-elon-musks-tesla-will-never-give-company-specific-incentives-in-ev-sector-says-government-official%2Farticleshow%2F105659927.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20unlikely%20to%20give%20specific%20incentives%20to%20any%20company%20in%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20sector%2C%20including%20Tesla.%20A%20government%20official%20has%20said%20that%20if%20incen