em%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Bhathiyaras%20(27%2C263%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20basic%20tenets%20and%20scriptures%20of%20Islam%2C%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20between%20the%20rich%20or%20poor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20discrimination%20does%20exist%20among%20certain%20followers%20of%20Islam%20who%20created%20three%20categories%2C%20Ashraf%2C%20Azlaf%20and%20Arzal.%20Bhathiyara%20is%20a%20caste%20group%20found%20mainly%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20group%E2%80%99s%20name%20itself%20is%20often%20used%20as%20an%20abuse.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20this%20abuse%20is%20hurled%20at%20anyone%20in%20public%20and%20few%20oppose%20it%2C%20not%20even%20the%20B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehathiyaras%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20419px)%2085vw%2C%20419px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20in%20order%20to%20protest%20one%20needs%20numerical%20strength.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20according%20to%20the%20caste-based%20census%20report%202022%20recently%20released%20by%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20current%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20is%20merely%2027%2C263.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20claim%20that%20most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20landless.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELack%20of%20numbers%20alone%20is%20not%20the%20reason%20for%20their%20social%20neglect.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%20caste%20which%20works%20with%20leather%20has%20a%20population%20of%206%2C869%2C664%20which%20is%20a%20significant%20number%20and%20has%20political%20implications.%20Yet%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20are%20treated%20as%20untouchable%20and%20the%20name%20of%20this%20caste%20is%20also%20often%20used%20as%20an%20invective%20despite%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20being%20in%20force%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20prohibits%20social%20humiliation%20of%20such%20castes.%20Also%2C%20those%20who%20take%20care%20of%20cattle%20and%20earn%20their%20living%20by%20milking%20them%20are%20berated%20as%20%E2%80%98gowar%E2%80%99%2C%20even%20though%20they%20have%20the%20highest%20population%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%2016%2C500%2C119.%20In%20terms%20of%20share%20in%20the%20population%2C%20it%20is%2014.266%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhathiyara%20may%20be%20an%20insult%20for%20the%20rich%2C%20but%20for%20those%20who%20belong%20to%20this%20caste%2C%20it%20is%20an%20important%20term%20recognised%20by%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20This%20caste%20group%20is%20categorised%20as%20an%20extremely%20backward%20class%20in%20Bihar%20and%20backward%20class%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20They%20mainly%20live%20in%20UP%2C%20Bihar%20and%20in%20parts%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20claim%20that%20their%20ancestors%20were%20brought%20(to%20India)%20by%20the%20Mughals.%20They%20are%20categorised%20as%20a%20backward%20class%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Since%20Jharkhand%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Bihar%20before%202000%2C%20they%20are%20present%20there%20as%20well%20and%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20same%20category%20as%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20also%20inhabit%20parts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20having%20probably%20migrated%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20Satna%20region%20in%20search%20of%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20now%20begun%20using%20the%20surname%20%E2%80%98Farooqui%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20%E2%80%98Sheikh%20Farooqui%E2%80%99.%20But%20they%20are%20still%20considered%20Bhathiyara%20in%20government%20documents%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20social%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESurprisingly%2C%20this%20caste%20group%20is%20associated%20with%20Sher%20Shah%20Suri%2C%20who%20defeated%20Humayun%20and%20captured%20Delhi.%20A%20tomb%20built%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20this%20ruler%20is%20still%20present%20in%20Sasaram%2C%20Bihar.%20Sher%20Shah%20Suri%20ordered%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Grand%20Trunk%20Road%20which%20directly%20connected%20Calcutta%20to%20Kabul%20in%20Afghanistan.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20road%2C%20Bhathiyaras%20were%20handed%20over%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20inns%20built%20along%20it.%20Even%20today%20there%20is%20a%20place%20in%20Delhi%20called%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%20which%20must%20have%20been%20an%20inn%20to%20stop%20by%20before%20one%20entered%20the%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20historical%20references%20are%20present%20at%20several%20places.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20is%20more%20in%20Allahabad%20and%20Fatehpur.%20Meanwhile%2C%20one%20can%20come%20across%20a%20Bhatiyara%20even%20randomly%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Central%20Bihar%20while%20in%20Rajasthan%20they%20mainly%20reside%20in%20Alwar%2C%20Bharatpur%2C%20Sikar%2C%20Jhunjhunu%2C%20Bikaner%2C%20Churu%20and%20Nagaur%20districts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20their%20occupation%20was%20to%20take%20care%20of%20inns%20but%20things%20changed%20with%20time.%20After%20the%20death%20of%20Sher%20Shah%20Suri%2C%20they%20continued%20working%20as%20innkeepers%20till%20the%20last%20ruler%20of%20this%20dynasty%2C%20his%20brother%20Salim%20Shah%20Suri.%20But%20when%20the%20Mughals%20re-conquered%2C%20they%20considered%20the%20community%20only%20worthy%20of%20pity.%20They%20were%20ousted%20from%20the%20inns%20and%20revenge%20was%20exacted%20from%20them%20for%20their%20service%20to%20Sher%20Shah%20Suri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20history%20was%20never%20viewed%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20deprived%20and%20the%20conquered%20and%20so%20was%20true%20for%20the%20innkeepers.%20Those%20who%20once%20took%20pride%20in%20calling%20themselves%20Afghans%20accepted%20the%20supremacy%20of%20the%20Mughals.%20In%20some%20places%20they%20still%20consider%20themselves%20as%20Ashraf%2C%20like%20Sheikh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20time%20does%20not%20stay%20the%20same%20for%20anyone.%20Neither%20did%20the%20time%20of%20Sher%20Shah%20Suri%20last%20long%2C%20nor%20did%20that%20of%20the%20Mughals.%20These%20people%20have%20also%20changed%20with%20time.%20The%20innkeepers%20of%20yore%20are%20now%20forced%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20by%20laying%20bricks%20in%20brick%20kilns%20and%20selling%20old%20clothes%20and%20utensils.%20A%20piece%20of%20land%20is%20still%20something%20Bhathiyaras%20are%20deprived%20of