3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20leaders%20are%20gathering%20today%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20for%20the%20opening%20of%20COP28%2C%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20global%20warming%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKing%20Charles%20and%20Pope%20Francis%20are%20attending%20alongside%20delegates%20from%20200%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20core%20goal%20will%20be%20making%20better%20progress%20toward%20meeting%20the%20Paris%202015%20UN%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20Celsius%20a%20year%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20polluting%20nations%20%E2%80%94%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20China's%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20conspicuous%20by%20their%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22COP28%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6569c7a147f9ecb37d88fc78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20man%20walks%20past%20a%20COP28%20sign%20during%20the%20United%20Nations%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20on%20December%201%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ELUDOVIC%20MARIN%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20that%20Biden%20would%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20and%20following%20criticism%20of%20the%20decision%20announced%20a%20last-minute%20schedule%20change%20Wednesday%2C%20sending%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20in%20Biden's%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20most%20senior%20US%20official%20scheduled%20to%20attend%20had%20been%20US%20climate%20envoy%20John%20Kerry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20attended%20both%20of%20the%20previous%20UN%20climate%20summits%20but%20is%20facing%20criticism%20for%20his%20green%20policies%20from%20Republicans%2C%20while%20also%20facing%20pressure%20from%20younger%20Democratic%20voters%20to%20