20the%20talks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20sticking%20point%20in%20the%20talks%20is%20the%20reluctance%20of%20some%20countries%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20to%20agree%20to%20tough%20cuts%20in%20emissions%20that%20they%20say%20would%20hamper%20their%20economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXi%20and%20Biden%20are%20doing%20little%20to%20signal%20their%20commitment%20to%20sharing%20the%20burden%20of%20reducing%20the%20climate%20crisis%20equally%20by%20not%20attending%20the%20summit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F27%2Fclimate%2Fbiden-cop28-climate-dubai.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share%26referringSource%3DarticleShare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esay%20critics.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%20over%20secret%20oil%20deals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20it%20even%20began%2C%20the%20COP28%20conference%20was%20clouded%20by%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20producers%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20and%20the%20COP28%20President%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20heads%20the%20Gulf%20State's%20oil%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20and%20Centre%20for%20Climate%20Reporting%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%2C%20citing%20briefing%20documents%2C%20reported%20that%20the%20UAE%20was%20planning%20to%20broker%20secret%20fossil%20fuel%20deals%20with%20nations%20attending%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-host-uae-broker-secret-oil-deals-climate-summit-bbc-2023-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520COP28%2520spokesman%2520told%2520Business%2Cunverified%2520documents%2520in%2520their%2520reporting.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fa%3ECOP28%20spokesman%20denied%20that%20the%20documents%20outlining%20the%20planned%20deals%20had%20in%20fact%20been%20discussed%20in%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Global%20Stocktake%3