0Ram%20Navami%2C%20Mahavir%20Jayanti%2C%20Samrat%20Ashok%20Jayanti%2C%20and%20Veer%20Kunwar%20Singh%20Jayanti%20fall%20during%20the%20summer%20vacation%20that%20will%20start%20from%20April%2015%20to%20May%2015%20in%202024.%20Typically%2C%20not%20all%20these%20festivals%20are%20consistently%20included%20in%20a%20standard%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFestivals%20such%20as%20Eid-ul-Fitr%2C%20Eid-ul-Zoha%2C%20and%20Muharram%20are%20expected%20to%20fall%20on%20April%2010%2C%2011%2C%2012%3B%20June%2018%2C19%2C20%3B%20and%20July%2017%20and%2018%2C%20respectively.%20These%20festivals%20always%20feature%20in%20the%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%202023%20and%202024%20calendars%20have%20a%20total%20of%2060%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20education%20department%20issued%20the%20holiday%20calendars%2C%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20Facebook%20%E2%80%93%20was%20flooded%20with%20reports%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20has%20curtailed%20the%20holidays%20related%20to%20Hindu%20festivals%20and%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20the%20holidays%20for%20the%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20social%20media%20users%20suggested%20that%20this%20could%20be%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20%E2%80%9Cappease%E2%80%9D%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patna-based%20Hindi%20newspapers%20also%20echoed%20the%20same%20narrative%2C%20reporting%20that%20the%20holidays%20for%20the%20Muslim%20festivals%20have%20been%20increased%2C%20while%20those%20for%20the%20Hindus%20have%20been%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20headline%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnavbharattimes.indiatimes.com%2Fstate%2Fbihar%2Fpatna%2Framnavami-shivratri-janmashtami-rakshabandhan-holidays-cancelled-eid-bakrid-3-day-close-bihar-school-controversy-kk-pathak%2Farticleshow%2F105552354.cms%