20other%20cells.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20hope%20the%20biobots%20could%20one%20day%20travel%20around%20the%20body%20to%20heal%20cells.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20created%20tiny%20biological%20%26quot%3Brobots%26quot%3B%20from%20lung%20cells%20that%20they%20hope%20could%20one%20day%20travel%20around%20our%20bodies%2C%20regenerating%20damaged%20tissues%20and%20treating%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robots%2C%20called%20anthrobots%2C%20range%20in%20size%20from%20the%20width%20of%20a%20human%20hair%20to%20the%20point%20of%20a%20sharpened%20pencil%20and%20can%20self-assemble%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnow.tufts.edu%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fscientists-build-tiny-biological-robots-human-cells%23%3A~%3Atext%3DResearchers%2520at%2520Tufts%2520have%2520created%2Cdamage%2520in%2520a%2520lab%2520dish.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETuftsNow%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20created%20by%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20from%20Tufts%20and%20Harvard%20universities%20who%20altered%20the%20chemical%20composition%20of%20anonymously-donated%20lung%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20discovered%20that%20when%20they%20made%20cilia%20%E2%80%93%20tiny%20hair-like%20structures%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20cells%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eface%20outwards%2C%20they%20began%20moving.%20And%20when%20a%20cluster%20of%20anthrobots%2C%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuperbot%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20placed%20with%20damaged%20neuron%20cells%20it%20was%20able%20to%20encourage%20new%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20don't%20yet%20know%20how%20the%20cell%20regeneration%20occurs%2C%20but%20believe%20that%20the%20anthrobots%20could%20once%20day%20be%20used%20to%20clear%20blocked%20arteries%2C%20repair%20spinal%20cords%2C%20identify%20cancer%20cells%2C%20or%20deliver%20drugs%20to%20specific%20parts%20of%20the%20body%2C%20per%20TuftsNow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20research%2C%20published%20Thursday%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1002%2Fadvs.202303575%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdvanced%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raises%20new%20questions%20about%20how%20human%20cells%20assemble%20and%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20research%20team%20had%20previously%20created%20similar%20tiny%20robots%2C%20or%20xenobots%2C%20from%20cells%20sourced%20from%20embryos%20of%20the%20African%20clawed%20frog.%20But%20the%20anthrobots%20prove%20that%20cells%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20amphibian%20or%20embryonic%20to%20regenerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoauthor%20Michael%20Levin%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fworld%2Fliving-robots-from-human-cells-scn%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20this%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20being%20an%20embryo.%20This%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20being%20a%20frog.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20much%20more%20general%20property%20of%20living%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlhough%20they're%20created%20from%20human%20cells%2C%20Levin%20said%20the%20anthrobots%20didn't%20have%20a%20full%20life%20cycle%20and%20so%20aren't%20considered%20as%20fully-fledged%20organisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20reminds%20us%20that%20these%20harsh%20binary%20categories%20that%20we've%20operated%20with%20%E2%80%93%20is%20that%20a%20robot%2C%20is%20that%20an%20animal%2C%20is%20that%20a%20machine%3F%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20don't%20serve%20us%20very%20well.%20We%20need%20to%20get%20beyond%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Levin%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20doctors%20may%20not%20be%20using%20anthrobots%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20they're%20another%20example%20of%20advancements%20in%20medical%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20has%20already%20approved%20more%20than%20500%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-genetic-