%20world%20for%20allegedly%20not%20being%20able%20to%20reduce%20its%20reliance%20on%20coal-based%20energy%20fast%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20along%20with%20China%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20oppose%20any%20discussion%20or%20decision%20that%20were%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20conference%20which%20could%20potentially%20put%20strictures%20on%20coal-fired%20power%20stations.%20France%20and%20the%20United%20States%20are%20expected%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20on%20private%20financing%20of%20these%20plants%20at%20the%20COP28%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKwatra%20said%20India%20is%20among%C2%A0a%20handful%20of%20large%20economies%20that%20are%20on%20track%20to%20fulfil%20all%20their%20climate%20commitments.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20major%20economies%20that%20is%20well%20on%20track%20to%20complete%20its%20obligated%20NDCs%20(Nationally%20Determined%20Contributions).%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20had%20announced%20and%20upgraded%20our%20NDCs%20last%20year%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20we%20are%20now%20well%20on%20our%20way%20even%20to%20meet%20those%20upgraded%20NDC%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcop28-not-giving-up-on-coal-anytime-soon-india-9049379%2F%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20is%20hoping%20for%20a%20clear%20roadmap%20on%20climate%20financing%20at%20the%20COP28%2C%20while%20affirming%20that%20it%20has%20always%20been%20upfront%20about%20its%20support%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Closs-and-damage%E2%80%9D%20fund.%20The%20fund%20in%20question%20helps%20countries%20recover%20from%20environmental%20degradation%20caused%20by%20industrial%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLoss%20and%20damage%20fund%20will%20be%20of%20great%20benefit%20to%20developing%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20proactive%20in%20taking%20practical%20climate%20action%20measures%2C%20an