ia's%20population%20is%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20population%2C%20but%20in%20global%20carbon%20emissions%20India%20is%20only%20at%204%20per%20cent.%20We%20are%20moving%20fast%20in%20achieving%20the%20NDC%20targets.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20reached%20our%20non-fossil%20fuel%20targets%20nine%20years%20before%20the%20deadline%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contribution%20(NDC)%2C%20a%20climate%20action%20plan%20to%20cut%20emissions%20and%20adapt%20to%20climate%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20much%20time%20to%20correct%20the%20mistakes%20of%20the%20last%20century%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20and%20asked%20every%20nation%20to%20work%20sincerely%20to%20meet%20their%20NDC%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20(COP)%20is%20a%20decision-making%20body%20that%20reviews%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(UNFCCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Environment%20Ministry%20has%20introduced%20two%20initiatives%20that%20indicate%20India's%20proactive%20approach%20to%20tackling%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20sustainability%20take%20forward%20'LiFE'%20-%20'Lifestyle%20for%20Environment'%20movement%20announced%20by%20PM%20Modi%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20credit%26quot%3B%20initiative%20seeks%20to%20encourage%20environmentally%20friendly%20practices%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20and%20conservation%20reflecting%20the%20ideas%20of%20the%20'LiFE'%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20among%20a%20few%20countries%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20its%20NDCs%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20degree%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20the%20only%20leader%20to%20join%20the%20opening%20plenary%20along%20with%20COP28%20President%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20and%20UN%20Climate%20Change%20president%20Simon%20Steill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20called%20for%20maintaining%20a%20balance%20between%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation%2C%20and%20said%20energy%20transition%20across%20the%20world%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Bjust%20and%20inclusive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20for%20rich%20countries%20to%20transfer%20technology%20to%20help%20emerging%20economies%20fight%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701429900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F01a3odpo_narendra-modi-cop28_625x300_01_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-contributes-less-than-4-to-global-carbon-emissions-pm-modi-at-cop28-4624249%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20called%20on%20all%20nations%20to%20work%20together%20to%20cut%20global%20emissions%20drastically.%20At%20the%20COP28%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20PM%20Modi%20today%20said%20India's%20emissions%20are%20very%20low%20compared%20to%20other%20nations%20whose%20population%20is%20much%20less.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-contributes-less-than-4-to-global-carbon-emissions-pm-modi-at-cop28-4624249%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-contributes-less-than-4-to-global-carbon-emissions-pm-modi-at-cop28-4624249%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-contributes-less-than-4-to-global-carbon-emissions-pm-modi-at-cop28-4624249%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Incredible%20Story%20Of%20Emma%20Carey%2C%20Who%20Survived%2014%2C000-Feet%20Fall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20skydiver%20survived%20a%20fall%20from%2014%2C000%20feet%20and%20the%20video%20of%20her%20incredible%20story%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Emma%20Carey%20said%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20she%20was%20on%20vacation%20in%20Switzerland%20in%202013.%20Speaking%20to%20news.com.au%2C%20Ms%20Carey%20said%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20Jemma%20Mrdak%20was%20against%20skydiving.%20But%20the%20thrill%20and%20excitement%20of%20the%20extreme%20sport%20drew%20Ms%20Carey%20towards%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20thrilling%20experience%20for%20then-20-year-old%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%20after%20complications%20with%20her%20parachute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%20surely%20I've%20died%2C%20like%20surely%20this%20is%20it.%20And%20then%20the%20next%20feeling%20that%20I%20had%20was%20just%20the%20most%20intense%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20clip%20that%20has%20amassed%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThat's%20insane..%3Cbr%3E%5CnCan't%20believe%20it%3Cbr%3E%5CnSurvive%2014%2C000%20ft%20fall%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%98%B2%20%F0%9F%98%AF%F0%9F%A4%AF%F0%9F%A4%AF%F0%9F%A4%AF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPRYGrVROOe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPRYGrVROOe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dedoyin%20(%40rheelz1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frheelz1%2Fstatus%2F1729936227980259491%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20jumped%20out%20(of%20a%20helicopter)%2C%20I%20was%20loving%20it.%20And%20so%20I%20felt%20my%20instructor's%20tap%20on%20my%20shoulder%20who%20asked%20me%20to%20cross%20my%20arms.%20That's%20when%20they%20were%20meant%20to%20pull%20the%20parachute.%20But%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20I%20was%20like%20'Okay.%20Well%2C%20I'm%20sure%20he's%20doing%20everything%20he%20can'.%20But%20then%20the%20moment%20I%20really%20realised%20was%20when%20I%20saw%20a%20scrunched%20up%20parachute%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Carey%20said%20at%20a%20po