has%20written%20some%20rumour%20and%20scuttlebutt%20that%20has%20made%20various%20claims%20about%20His%20Majesty%20the%20King%20that%20are%2C%20frankly%2C%20completely%20unproven%2C%26quot%3B%20UK%20Security%20Minister%20Tom%20Tugendhat%20told%20TalkTV%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20King's%20done%20a%20brilliant%20job%20for%20us%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20last%20year%20since%20he's%20been%20King%2C%20but%20he's%20been%20absolutely%20fantastic%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years%20in%20arguing%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20British%20people%20as%20Prince%20of%20Wales.%20So%20frankly%20I%20see%20this%20as%20just%20rumour%2C%20hearsay%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20disparage%20somebody%20who's%20served%20our%20country%20with%20enormous%20dignity%20and%20enormous%20grace%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dutch%20publisher%20of%20the%20new%20book%2C%20Xander%20Uitgevers%2C%20said%20it%20had%20been%20pulled%20from%20shelves%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20due%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Berror%26quot%3B.%20Scobie%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20been%20insisting%20it%20was%20not%20part%20of%20some%20publicity%20stunt%20and%20lamented%20that%20the%20row%20had%20%26quot%3Bovershadowed%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20of%20his%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20is%20frustrating%20because%20it%20feeds%20into%20something%20that%20couldn't%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%20And%20also%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20I've%20always%20felt%20the%20names%20weren't%20needed%20to%20have%20this%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writer%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20co-authored%20another%20book%20on%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20entitled%20'Finding%20Freedom'%2C%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20cheerleader%20of%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20ever%20since%20they%20stepped%20back%20from%20frontline%20royalty%20back%20in%202020%20and%20relocated%20to%20California.%20He%20has%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20or%20interview%20the%20couple%20for%20the%20latest%20book.%20Representatives%20of%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20have%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20book's%20release%20or%20the%20ensuing%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20interview%20in%20March%202021%2C%20Meghan%20told%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20that%20Harry%20had%20been%20asked%20by%20an%20unnamed%20family%20member%20%26quot%3Bhow%20dark%26quot%3B%20their%20son%20Archie's%20skin%20might%20be.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Buckingham%20Palace%20called%20the%20allegation%20%26quot%3Bconcerning%26quot%3B%20and%20Prince%20William's%20spokesperson%20categorically%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bracism%20has%20no%20place%20in%20our%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20subsequent%20interview%2C%20his%20younger%20brother%20Prince%20Harry%20was%20asked%20whether%20he%20would%20describe%20the%20comment%20about%20his%20son's%20skin%20colour%20as%20racist%20and%20he%20told%20ITV%20that%20he%20wouldn't%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20a%20difference%20between%20%26quot%3Bracism%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunconscious%20bias%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701428700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F9eopm85o_king-charles-camilla-650_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbuckingham-palace-exploring-all-options-as-king-embroiled-in-race-row-4624214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buckingham%20Palace%20officials%20said%20today%20that%20they%20were%20exploring%20all%20options%2C%20including%20legal%2C%20as%20King%20Charles%20III%20and%20Kate%20Middleton%20-%20the%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20were%20embroiled%20in%20a%20race%20row%20after%20the%20Dutch%20edition%20of%20a%20controversial%20