0be%20ambitious%20and%20energy%20transition%20should%20be%20innovative%2C%20equal%2C%20and%20equitable.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20transfer%20of%20technology%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20has%20pushed%20for%20alternate%20fuels%20through%20hydrogen%20fuel%20and%20biofuel%20alliances.%20In%20Glasgow%2C%20a%20mission%20life%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20vision%20was%20put%20forward.%20Today%2C%20from%20this%20forum%20I%20announce%20a%20green%20credit%20initiative.%20I%20hope%20you%20will%20join%20this%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMother%20Earth%20is%20looking%20toward%20us%20to%20protect%20her%20future.%20We%20have%20to%20succeed.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20decisive%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20do%20not%20have%20much%20time%20to%20correct%20the%20mistakes%20of%20the%20last%20century%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701428400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fcsojcm_pm-at-cop28-pti_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-gave-model-of-development-to-world-pm-modis-top-quotes-at-cop28-4624341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20at%20the%20COP28%20World%20Climate%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%20today%20and%20proposed%20to%20host%20the%20COP33%20summit%20in%202028%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-gave-model-of-development-to-world-pm-modis-top-quotes-at-cop28-4624341%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-gave-model-of-development-to-world-pm-modis-top-quotes-at-cop28-4624341%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-gave-model-of-development-to-world-pm-modis-top-quotes-at-cop28-4624341%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Match%20Factory%20Launches%20Remastered%20Fatih%20Akin%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Crossing%20the%20Bridge%20%E2%80%93%20T