0air%20sacs%20in%20the%20lungs.%20This%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20breathe.%20ARDS%20can%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20pneumonia%2C%20sepsis%2C%20and%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-white-lung-syndrome-spreads-globally-cases-reported-worldwide-4624209%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Mysterious%20White%20Lung%20Syndrome%20Spreads%20Globally%2C%20Cases%20Reported%20Worldwide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPulmonary%20alveolar%20microlithiasis%20(PAM)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20rare%20lung%20disease%20that%20is%20caused%20by%20deposits%20of%20calcium%20in%20the%20air%20sacs%20of%20the%20lungs.%20This%20can%20cause%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20coughing%2C%20and%20chest%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilicosis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20lung%20disease%20that%20is%20caused%20by%20inhaling%20silica%20dust.%20Silica%20dust%20is%20found%20in%20sand%2C%20stone%2C%20and%20other%20materials.%20Silicosis%20can%20cause%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20coughing%2C%20and%20chest%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20symptoms%20of%20white%20lung%20syndrome%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20lung%20syndrome%20symptoms%20differ%20based%20on%20the%20cause%2C%20but%20common%20signs%20include%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20coughing%2C%20chest%20pain%2C%20fever%2C%20and%20fatigue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20underlying%20cause%20of%20white%20lung%20syndrome%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20cause%20of%20white%20lung%20syndrome%20is%20still%20being%20investigated%2C%20but%20it%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20combination%20of%20bacterial%2C%20viral%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors.%20Viruses%2C%20such%20as%20influenza%20or%20COVID-19%2C%20can%20cause%20white%20lung%20syndrome%20by%20damaging%20the%20lungs'%20air%20sacs.%20Bacteria%2C%20such%20as%20Mycop