next%20two%20years%2C%20with%20work%20underway%20to%20plug%20gaps%20in%20about%2060%20km%20stretch%20along%20these%20two%20fronts.%20Shah%20was%20speaking%20after%20taking%20salute%20from%20a%20ceremonial%20parade%20of%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20its%2059th%20Raising%20Day%20celebrations%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20fenced%20and%20plugged%20gaps%20in%20about%20560%20km%20of%20the%20India-Pakistan%20and%20India-Bangladesh%20borders%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20since%20it%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20all%20the%20gaps%20in%20these%20two%20borders%20on%20India's%20western%20and%20eastern%20flank%20respectively%20are%20being%20plugged%20and%20work%20in%20only%20about%2060%20km%20is%20continuing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20two%20years%20we%20will%20entirely%20secure%20these%20two%20borders%2C%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20borders--%202%2C290%20km%20of%20the%20India-Pakistan%20International%20Border%20and%204%2C096%20km%20of%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border--%20are%20marked%20by%20long%20riverine%2C%20mountainous%20and%20marshy%20areas%20where%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20erect%20fences%20and%20hence%20the%20BSF%20and%20other%20agencies%20use%20technical%20gadgets%20to%20check%20infiltration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20firmly%20believe%20that%20a%20country%20cannot%20develop%20and%20prosper%20if%20its%20borders%20are%20not%20secure...the%20government%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20led%20the%20country%20to%20the%20moon%20with%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%2C%20G20%20Summit%20and%20brought%20the%20economy%20from%20the%2011th%20to%20the%20fifth%20spot%2C%20and%20this%20was%20all%20possible%20due%20to%20our%20forces%20deployed%20for%20securing%20the%20borders%20like%20the%20BSF%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%2C%20the%20BSF%2C%20are%20the%20essential%20pillar%20of%20this%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20told%20the%20BSF%20personnel%20at%20the%20'Meru'%20training%20camp%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20the%20border%20fence%20does%20not%20alone%20protect%20the%20country%2C%20it%20only%20helps%20in%20rendering%20this%20task.%20It%20is%20the%20brave%20BSF%20jawan%20who%20does%20this%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20border%20force%2C%20about%202.65%20lakh%20in%20strength%2C%20was%20raised%20on%20December%201%2C%201965%2C%20and%20is%20primarily%20tasked%20to%20guard%20the%20over%206%2C386%20km-long%20Indian%20fronts%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20minister%20asserted%20that%20whenever%20a%20BJP%20government%20took%20the%20reins%20of%20power%20in%20the%20country%2C%20border%20security%20was%20prioritised%2C%20from%20the%20government%20of%20former%20PM%20A%20B%20Vajpayee%20to%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Atal%20Ji's%20(Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee)%20government%20brought%20a%20%26quot%3Bintegrated%26quot%3B%20approach%20for%20border%20security%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20assimilated%20security%2C%20development%20and%20democratic%20processes%20along%20with%20strong%20infrastructure%20and%20initiation%20of%20welfare%20measures%20for%20the%20local%20population%20living%20on%20the%20front%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strengthened%20rail%2C%20road%2C%20waterways%20and%20telephone%20communication%20connectivity%20apart%20from%20land%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20minister%20said%20his%20government%20created%20452%20new%20border%20posts%2C%20510%20observation%20towers%2C%20got%20electricity%20connection%20to%20637%20borders%20posts%20while%20500%20such%20facilities%20were%20linked%20with%20piped%20water%20across%20various%20fronts%20over%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Left%20Wing%20Extremism%2