E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20indictment%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20unsealed%20on%20Wednesday%20(November%2029)%20said%20that%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20directed%20a%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20an%20unnamed%2C%20pro-Khalistan%20political%20activist%20on%20US%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20had%20reportedly%20said%20earlier%20that%20their%20government%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-thwarts-plot-kill-sikh-separatist-issues-warning-india-ft-2023-11-22%2F%5C%22%3Ethwarted%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20and%20lawyer%20of%20US%20and%20Canadian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22From%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20says%20that%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20worked%20with%20a%20man%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20to%20orchestrate%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%20Their%20alleged%20bid%20failed%20as%20their%20contacts%2C%20including%20the%20proposed%20hitman%2C%20were%20working%20with%20or%20for%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20the%20indictment%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20Gupta%20suggested%20to%20the%20undercover%20officer%20that%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fterrorism-accused-hardeep-singh-nijjar-shot-to-death-in-surrey-bc-gurdwara%5C%22%3Ewho%20was%20murdered%20in%20Canada%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20also%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctarget%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%20that%20his%20government%20was%20pursuing%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20that%20Indian%20government%20agents%20may%20have%20been%20linked%20with%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20murder%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-confirms-withdrawal-of-41-diplomats-from-india-visa-processing-time-to-go-up%5C%22%3Esparking%20a%20diplomatic%20standoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Canada%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhurshid%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20while%20Canada-India%20relations%20had%20experienced%20their%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20recent%20allegations%20were%20%E2%80%9Cworrisome%E2%80%9D%20owing%20to%20better%20relations%20between%20it%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20happened%20with%20Canada%2C%20we%20%5BIndia%5D%20reacted%20and%20said%20this%20is%20nonsense%2C%20this%20is%20rubbish%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20concern%20that%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20were%20sort%20of%20agreeing%20with%20Canada%20that%20there%20was%20need%20for%20some%20clarification%20and%20need%20for%20some%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20isolation%20one%20incident%20and%20one%20event%20in%20Canada%20etc%20%E2%80%A6%20can%20be%20understood%20that%20there%20may%20be%20a%20difference%20of%20perception%20and%20that%20is%20causing%20this%20trouble.%20But%20now%20this%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20US%20%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20worrisome%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khurshid%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20our%20relations%20with%20Canada%2C%20which%20have%20been%20a%20little%20strained%20and%20stressed%20in%20the%20past%2C%20our%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20have%20been%20very%20smooth%20and%20very%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20while%20there%20are%20concerns%20about%20pro-Khalistan%20activists%20operating%20from%20abroad%2C%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20officials%20are%20%E2%80%9Cproactively%20trying%20to%20interfere%20with%20what%20the%20Western%20democracies%20consider%20to%20be%20entitlements%20and%20rights%20that%20citizens%20have%E2%80%9D%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20troubling%20thing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20we%20should%20have%20been%20extra%20careful%20about%20this.%20That%20we%20should%20not%20have%20allowed%20anybody%20to%20raise%20any%20questions%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20uprightness.%20Why%20this%20is%20happening%20is%20worrisome%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20former%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20external%20affairs%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20%E2%80%9Ca%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20that%20warrants%20a%20comprehensive%20internal%20inquiry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20post-indictment%20reaction%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%5C%22%3Eexternal%20affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20US%20government%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20were%20%E2%80%9Ca%20matter%20of%20concern%E2%80%9D%20and%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccontrary%20to%20government%20policy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701423511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01150719%2FFotoJet.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-leaders-on-pannun-indictment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20externa