very%20corner%2C%20he%20has%20the%20licence%20to%20be%20as%20boorish%20as%20he%20wants%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protagonist%20(Ranbir%20Kapoor)%20goes%20hell%20for%20leather%2C%20spills%20tons%20of%20blood%2C%20kills%20tens%20of%20people%20and%20blows%20hot%20and%20hotter%20when%20he%20figures%20out%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20is%20indeed%20afoot%20to%20eliminate%20the%20patriarch%20and%20rob%20his%20family%20of%20the%20steel%20plant%20that%20it%20owns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20love%2C%20there%20is%20no%20room%20for%20niceties%20for%20this%20my-way-or-the-highway%20guy.%20He%20does%20not%20so%20much%20as%20fall%20in%20love%20as%20make%20a%20grab%20for%20it.%20He%20does%20not%20propose%20marriage.%20He%20literally%20demands%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20he%20appears%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20is%20unquestioning%20allegiance%20from%20the%20girl%2C%20Geetanjali%20(Rashmika%20Mandanna)%2C%20who%20he%20had%20the%20hots%20for%20as%20a%20schoolboy%20but%20hasn't%20met%20since%20his%20angry%20dad%2C%20Balbir%20Singh%2C%20packed%20him%20off%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20seeing%20him%20turn%20a%20new%20leaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nothing%20changes.%20Ranvijay%20Singh%20is%20back%20and%20he%20is%20worse%20than%20ever%20before.%20The%20lady%20plays%20along%20without%20a%20whimper.%20Not%20only%20does%20she%20not%20demonstrate%20any%20sort%20of%20willpower%20of%20her%20own%2C%20she%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20thrilled%20at%20the%20prospect%20of%20being%20swept%20away%20from%20her%20engagement%20party%20and%20hustled%20into%20a%20marriage%20against%20her%20parents'%20wishes.%20He%20own%20does%20not%20count%20for%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20she%20does%20not%20have%20a%20voice%20but%20her%20utterances%20and%20positions%20are%20mere%20reactions%20to%20what%20the%20man%20in%20her%20life%20does%20entirely%20of%20his%20own%20volition%20and%20then%20feigns%20that%20his%20actions%20are%20consensual.%20When%20he%20strays%20from%20his%20wife%20and%20develops%20a%20bond%20with%20another%20girl%20(Triptii%20Dimri)%2C%20he%20proffers%20the%20kind%20of%20untenable%20logic%20that%20only%20a%20man%20like%20him%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20hero%20is%20the%20way%20that%20he%20is%2C%20can%20the%20antagonist%20(Bobby%20Deol%2C%20who%20struggles%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20in%20a%20severely%20abbreviated%20appearance)%20be%20any%20different%3F%20He%20is%20not.%20The%20bad%20guy%20-%20he%20lives%20in%20faraway%20Scotland%20and%20pretty%20much%20does%20whatever%20his%20damaged%20heart%20desires%20-%20pops%20up%20after%20%3Ci%3EAnimal%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20run%20well%20over%20half%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20be%20left%20behind%2C%20the%20vicious%20villain%20spares%20no%20effort%20to%20prove%20that%20he%20is%20as%20bloodthirsty%20as%20Ranvijay%20Singh%2C%20the%20scion%20of%20the%20business%20group%20that%20owns%20Swastik%20Steel.%20The%20two%20men%20are%20caught%20in%20a%20deadly%20blood%20feud.%20A%20vile%20attack%20on%20Balbir%20Singh%20(Anil%20Kapoor)%20by%20men%20who%20want%20to%20wrest%20control%20of%20the%20ageing%20tycoon's%20business%20empire%20elicits%20a%20reprisal%20so%20venomous%20that%20is%20triggers%20an%20unending%20cycle%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20justify%20that%20it%20is%20a%20man's%20world%2C%20%3Ci%3EAnimal%3C%2Fi%3E%20presents%20two%20men%20who%20are%20as%20physically%20impaired%20as%20they%20are%20mentally%20scarred.%20One%20loses%20all%20sense%20of%20taste%20and%20smell%20and%20is%20unable%20to%20hear%20after%20sustaining%20six%20bullet%20wounds%20that%20push%20his%20heart%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20cannot%20speak.%20He%20communicates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20brother%20who%20serves%20as%20a%20sign%20language%20interpreter.%20When%20the%20two%20men%20square%20off%20in%20the%20climax%20-%20it%20is%2C%20like%20such%20clashes%20usually%20are%20in%20vengeance%20sagas%20of%20this%20sort%2C%20staged%20on%20th