0Islam%E2%80%99s%20most-revered%20prophet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20students%20(boys%20and%20girls)%20are%20directed%20to%20leave%20the%20campus%2F%20hostel%20by%20or%20before%2010%20am%20tomorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20dean%2C%20students%20welfare%2C%20NIT%20on%20November%2030.%20The%20institute%20has%20also%20suspended%20mess%20service%20in%20the%20campus%20from%20Friday%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20has%20also%20asked%20other%20colleges%20in%20the%20region%20to%20shut%20down%20classrooms%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20early%20onset%20of%20winter%E2%80%9D%20and%20shift%20their%20academic%20activities%20to%20the%20online%20mode%20only%2C%20with%20police%20apprehensive%20of%20law%20and%20order%20deterioration%20due%20to%20the%20allegedly%20blasphemous%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hurriedly%20announced%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%2030%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20R.R.%20Swain%20said%20that%20a%20case%20(FIR%20No.156%2F23)%20under%20Sections%20295-A%20(insulting%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%2C%20153A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20religious%20groups)%20and%20153%20(provoking%20riots)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20has%20been%20registered%20at%20Nigeen%20police%20station%20on%20November%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwain%20didn%E2%80%99t%20divulge%20information%20about%20whether%20the%20accused%20student%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Maharashtra%20who%20had%20fled%20the%20campus%20after%20uploading%20the%20post%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Without%20naming%20Pakistan%2C%20he%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20being%20hatched%20%E2%80%9Cacross%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20to%20use%20the%20prevailing%20anger%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20%E2%80%9Cother%20things%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20probe%20suggests%20that%20many%20social%20media%20handles%20were%20created%20across%20the%20border%20(after%20the%20NIT%20student%20shared%20the%20controversial%20post)%20to%20stir%20tensions%20in%20Kashmir.%20Their%20messages%20are%20designed%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20trigger%20violence.%20Some%20elements%20here%20mix%20with%20them%20to%20disturb%20peace%20and%20harmony%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swain%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20taken%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20open%20source%20intelligence%20networks%20followed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20several%20social%20media%20handles%20were%20interested%20in%20spotlighting%20the%20Hindu%20identity%20of%20the%20student%20who%20had%20uploaded%20the%20offensive%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20purportedly%20to%20stir%20communal%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20posts%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20suggested%20that%20the%20accused%20student%20was%20having%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20local%20girl%2C%20whose%20purported%20photos%20were%20also%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20while%20some%20of%20these%20posts%20called%20on%20other%20students%20in%20Kashmir%20to%20boycott%20non-local%20students%20and%20%E2%80%9Cteach%20them%20a%20lesson%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%2C%20an%20old%20video%20was%20used%20as%20showcasing%20the%20recent%20protests%20that%20erupted%20in%20NIT%20Srinagar%20and%20parts%20of%20Kashmir%20against%20the%20blasphemous%20post.%20Some%20of%20these%20posts%20on%20X%20were%20shared%20by%20handles%20which%20were%20created%20in%20the%20month%20of%20November%2C%20raising%20eyebrows%20in%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDGP%20Swain%20said%20that%20the%20police%20was%20monitoring%20social%20media%20and%20%E2%80%9Cany%20misadventure%E2%80%A6done%20with%20deliberate%20and%20malicious%20intent%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20the%20framework%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CInnocent%20remarks%20on%20a%20situation%20as%20a%20viewpoint%20is%20certainly%20different%20which%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20part%20of%20any%20police%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20distinction%20between%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20the%20right%20to%20dissent.%20But%2C%20statements%20based%20on%20falsehoods%2C%20half-truths%20and%20out-of-context%20designed%20to%20further%20violence%20are%20certainly%20not%20in%20that%20category.%20We%20will%20make%20the%20distinction%20with%20the%20powerful%20tools%20of%20investigation%20and%20intelligence%20that%20we%20have.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGP%20said%20that%20the%20police%20was%20proposing%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20emergency%20law%E2%80%9D%20under%20Section%20144%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20that%20will%20criminalise%20uploading%20any%20content%20on%20social%20media%20which%20may%20affected%20communal%20harmony%20or%20disturb%20peace%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPosting%2C%20forwarding%20or%20sharing%20any%20type%20of%20content%20which%20disturbs%20communal%20harmony%20or%20is%20used%20to%20create%20fear%20or%20terrorise%20on%20social%20media%2C%20will%20become%20illegal%20and%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20inform%20police%20about%20such%20content%20before%20sharing%20it%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwain%20said%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20respects%20the%20honour%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20same%20way%20that%20we%20respect%20the%20honour%20of%20our%20country%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20our%20legal%20responsibility%20and%20in%20any%20situation%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20dignity%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%20to%20be%20besmirched.%20But%20we%20should%20be%20alert%20to%20the%20conspiracies%20at%20work%20to%20use%20this%20incident%20to%20flare%20up%20tensions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20while%20appealing%20citizens%20to%20restrain%20from%20indulging%20in%20any%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20mainstream%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20led%20by%20Mehboob%20Mufti%2C%20National%20Conference%2C%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chairman%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20and%20others%20condemned%20the%20allegedly%20blasphemous%20post%20while%20urging%20the%20authorities%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20NIT%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reverence%20and%20honour%20of%20the%20Holy%20Prophet%20(PBUH)%20is%20dearer%20to%20a%20Muslim%20than%20his%20or%20her%20life%20and%20such%20blasphemous%20remarks%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20by%20the%20Muslims%20of%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muttahida%20Majlis-e-Ulama%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(MMUJK)%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20of%20religious%20bodies%20headed%20by%20Mirwaiz%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MMUJK%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%20conduct%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthorough%20investigation%E2%80%A6into%20how%20and%20why%20this%20incident%20occurred%E2%80%9D%20while%20demanding%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20those%20found%20involved%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20brought%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Srinagar%20NIT%20has%20shot%20into%20the%20limelight%20due%20to%20a%20controversy%20involving%20students%20that%20boiled%20down%20into%20communal%20tensions.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20institute%20was%20closed%20for%20days%20after%20a%20face-off%20between%20two%20groups%20of%20students%20during%20an%20India-Pakistan%20cricket%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701419418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01135551%2FArial_-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnit-srinagar-closed-after-social-media-post-controversy-govt-asks-other-colleges-to-go-online%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20J%26amp%3BK%20DGP%20has%20said%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20being%20hatched%20%E2%80%9Cacross%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20to%20use%20the%20prevailing%20anger%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20%E2%80%9Cother%20things%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnit-srinagar-closed-after-social-media-post-controversy-govt-asks-other-colleges-to-go-online%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Sets%20Aside%20Reappointment%20of%20Kannur%20Uni%20VC%2C%20Cites%20Kerala%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Unwarranted%20Interference'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F29141656%2FLibrary_Science_-_1.original.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%2030%2C%20set%20aside%20the%20reappointment%20of%20Gopinath%20Ravindran%20as%20the%20vice-chancellor%20of%20Kannur%20University%2C%20saying%20the%20Kerala%20government%20made%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%20interference%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindran%20was%20the%20first%20vice%20chancellor%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20state%20to%20be%20re-appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fsupreme-court-quashes-reappointment-of-gopinath-ravindran-as-kannur-university-vice-chancellor%2Farticle67589878.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20delivered%20by%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%20The%20top%20court%20overturned%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20February%202022%20decision%20which%20upheld%20the%20validity%20of%20a%20November%2023%2C%202021%20notification%20reappointing%20Ravindran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20judgment%2C%20authored%20by%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20was%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%20interference%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20reappointment%20process%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20chancellor%20(the%20state%E2%80%99s%20governor)%20abdicating%2Fsurrendering%20his%20statutory%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Pardiwala%20read%20out%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20in%20court%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20higher%20education%20minister%20had%20initiated%20the%20reappointment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-ravindran-reappoint-vc-kannur-university-sc-9048295%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20impugned%20judgement%20and%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20high%20court%20dated%20February%2023%2C%202022%20is%20hereby%20set%20aside%20and%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%20the%20notification%20dated%20November%2023%2C%202021%20reappointing%20the%20respondent%20number%204%20(Ravindran)%20as%20the%20vice%20chancellor%20of%20the%20Kannur%20University%20is%20hereby%20set%20aside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kerala%20high%20court%20division%20bench%20had%20on%20February%2023%2C%202022%20dismissed%20an%20appeal%20against%20a%20single-judge%20order%20upholding%20Ravindran%E2%80%99s%20re-appointment.%20It%20said%20the%20appointment%20was%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20that%20he%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Can%20usurper%20to%20the%20post%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Equo%20warranto%3C%2Fem%3E%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20member%20of%20Kannur%20University%E2%80%99s%20senate%20another%20person%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Academic%20Council%20(Management%20Studies)%2C%20Kannur%20University.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20they%20claimed%20the%20reappointment%20wa